  "text": "Recent research works on Artificial Intelligence have proved that ANN paradigm can be succesfully applied to the Software Engineering domain and, in particular, to the field of estimation [CITATION_1] . The promising results obtained show notable consistency and exactitude. Several predictions related to software estimation are related to ANN. The work of [CITATION_2] shows an example of Bayesian regularization of an ANN for estimating the size of software developments. [CITATION_3] estimates the cost of the software by means of a Wavelet ANN. [CITATION_4] also predicts the reliability of the software by means of hybrid models, citing some of the most representative works in the field.",
